structured_output_contract:
Append exactly one JSON object to {{KRIS_DIR}}/challenge/codex_challenges.jsonl, schema:
{ "ref_id": "{{REF_ID}}", "bib_key": "{{BIB_KEY}}", "side": "codex", "challenge_response": "CONCEDE" | "REFUTE" | "STILL_UNCERTAIN", "final_verdict": "REAL" | "CHIMERIC" | "FAKE" | "UNCERTAIN", "final_confidence": 0.0-1.0, "rebuttal_summary": "1-3 sentences on what re-checking Claude's URLs revealed", "evidence": [ {"step": "refetch_claude_url", "url": "...", "result": "...", "quote": "..."} ] }
No other output. No markdown, no preamble.
